    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-cared-for vehicle that perfectly captures the balance between performance and everyday utility. The exterior finish remains vibrant and glossy, showing only the minor, superficial stone chips one would expect from light highway use. Inside, the cabin is a testament to quality; the leather seats remain supportive with minimal creasing, and every electronic feature\u2014from the touchscreen navigation to the heated seats\u2014operates exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and the transmission shifts seamlessly, backed by a consistent maintenance history and recent fluid service. The suspension is tight, and the brakes provide a confident, linear feel. This car has been smoke-free and garage-kept, ensuring it remains a reliable and sophisticated choice for its next owner. It is a solid, dependable example that is ready to drive away today.",
      "price": 32800.0,
